annotationA: Glucosylceramide synthase (GlcT-1) catalyzes the formation of glucosylceramide, the core component of glycosphingolipids. GlcT-1 regulates lipid energy metabolism in fat body and plays critical roles in embryo survival and development
annotationB: Putative neutral sphingomyelinase; Sphingomyelin phosphodiesterase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: sphingomyelin metabolic process
